snippet.title: Project+ v2.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Project+ is a community-driven patch for Project M, built on top of Project M 3.6 and Legacy TE 2.5.
It is aimed to further balance, bugfix, and polish Project M. For more information, including a changelog and downloads, check out our website! https://projectplusgame.com/

Download for Wii and Dolphin Netplay: https://projectplusgame.com/download/
Project+ Discord Server: https://projectplusgame.com/discord
Project M subreddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/ssbpm

Project M was a mod created by the Project M Dev Team (PMDT) that transformed the gameplay of Super Smash Bros. Brawl, inspired by Melee's gameplay.

The Project+ Development Team is not associated with the PMDT or Legacy TE teams, but we thank both teams for their incredible work.

Music:
Woody - Moonlight
Knuckles' Theme Special Remix - Tee Lopes feat. Jun Senoue

Trailer edited by HyperFlame.
